libs.content:
find_library( opencl_libraries
        names opencl
        hints
            ${opencl_root}/lib
            $env{amdappsdkroot}/lib
            $env{cuda_path}/lib
        doc "opencl dynamic library path"
        path_suffixes x86_64 x64
        paths
            /usr/lib
    )
